  "scope_statement": {
    "what_is_demonstrated": "Argument-adjunct asymmetry in mean dependency distance is confirmed in 3 verified spoken-written UD treebank pairs (Slovenian, French). Raw MDD differences are large. Pattern holds in 5/5 robustness variants.",
